title: Hypnosis Books
description:
Ok here is another large collection of Hypnosis/Hypnotherapy Ebooks that I have put together, not sure if any of them have been in any other torrents, so I apologise in advance for this. A couple of them have been converted to PDF from text files, so if any of them are incorrectly formatted I apologise for that too. Anyway, as usual, hope you find them a great resource for study or just want to collect them, either way, enjoy.



And please don't forget to sow the seeds, as many people may not have these and it would be a shame to let them waste away in the abyss that is the Internet
